@startuml Employee State Machine

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    BorderColor #37474F
    FontColor #212121
    StartColor #4CAF50
    EndColor #F44336
}

[*] --> CautiouslyOptimistic

state "Cautiously Optimistic" as CautiouslyOptimistic #C8E6C9 {
    CautiouslyOptimistic : entry / reports mood 7
    CautiouslyOptimistic : "Maybe this one will be different."
    CautiouslyOptimistic : Attends Wellness Wednesday voluntarily.
    CautiouslyOptimistic : Fills out surveys honestly.
}

state "Skeptical" as Skeptical #FFF9C4 {
    Skeptical : entry / reports mood 6 (actual: 5)
    Skeptical : "I've seen this before."
    Skeptical : Notices metrics don't map to reality.
    Skeptical : Begins strategic survey responses.
}

state "Resigned" as Resigned #FFE0B2 {
    Resigned : entry / reports mood 7 (actual: 4)
    Resigned : "It doesn't matter what I report."
    Resigned : Automates check-ins.
    Resigned : Gap between reported and actual mood: 3pts.
}

state "Actively Subverting" as ActivelySubverting #FFCCBC {
    ActivelySubverting : entry / reports mood 8 (actual: 3)
    ActivelySubverting : "If you can't beat the system, game it."
    ActivelySubverting : Joins metric optimization working group.
    ActivelySubverting : Trades wellness credits on black market.
}

state "Gaming the System" as GamingTheSystem #FFCDD2 {
    GamingTheSystem : entry / reports mood 9 (actual: 2)
    GamingTheSystem : "Wellness score: 94. Burnout level: critical."
    GamingTheSystem : Has perfected the art of visible engagement.
    GamingTheSystem : Is debugging production at 2am off-camera.
}

CautiouslyOptimistic --> Skeptical : Wellness Wednesday\nmandated;\nmeditation becomes\nperformance review
Skeptical --> Resigned : Transparency Dashboard\nlaunches; realizes\nscores affect\npromotion decisions
Resigned --> ActivelySubverting : Synergy Champions\nProgram creates\ntwo-tier culture;\n"Siloed" label applied
ActivelySubverting --> GamingTheSystem : Focus-Sprint Protocol\nfails spectacularly;\nChad logs it as\n"successful innovation"

' The ironic loop
GamingTheSystem -[#F44336,dashed]-> CautiouslyOptimistic : New VP of People\nhired; announces\n"Synergy Matrix 2.0"\n(the cycle repeats)

note right of GamingTheSystem
    **Terminal State (in practice)**

    Brenda reports mood 9
    while debugging a P0
    off-camera during
    "Mindful Moments."

    Her synergy score
    has never been higher.

    She has three interviews
    scheduled this week.
end note

note left of CautiouslyOptimistic
    **Week 1 of any new initiative.**
    This state has a half-life
    of approximately 2.3 sprints.
end note

@enduml
